long_description: we are a tight-knit family made up of laborers, operators, field specialists, project managers, and leaders. hi-way is a place to belong and thrive. our strength is in the relationships and reputation we've built doing good work, the right way. we share a common goal of delivering high-quality work on time, every time. for more than half a century, hi-way has built an outstanding reputation in the concrete paving and construction industry. founded in 1969, hi-way was built on a commitment to excellence in concrete paving and construction. since then, we have grown to compete in the state, federal, and military markets as a prime contractor, while continuing to act as a specialty concrete paving subcontractor. 1970s & 80s. hi-way moved away from existing as solely a subcontractor and became a full-service general contractor. our first jobs as a prime contractor involved extensive rebuilding and new construction of major highways in that same area around ohio, from indianapolis, in, to pittsburgh, pa, and from youngstown, oh, to beckley, wv.
